skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: periodic table
des:
This is a new Alexa skill to provide information about the periodic table elements like Aluminum, Calcium, Carbon ...etc.
You can just say: "Alexa, open periodic table and give me an element." and the skill will provide you the information about one of the elements randomly.
